{
  "page": "Torrence Teague",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Teague\" title=\"House Teague\"><img alt=\"House Teague.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b0/House_Teague.svg/50px-House_Teague.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b0/House_Teague.svg/75px-House_Teague.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b0/House_Teague.svg/100px-House_Teague.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> King</span><br />Torrence Teague</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Teague\" title=\"House Teague\"><img alt=\"House Teague.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b0/House_Teague.svg/50px-House_Teague.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b0/House_Teague.svg/75px-House_Teague.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b0/House_Teague.svg/100px-House_Teague.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Monarch</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Full name</th><td>\nTorrence I Teague</td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Titles</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Lord\" title=\"Lord\">Lord</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Trident\" title=\"King of the Trident\">King of the Trident</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Personal Information</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Race</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Andal\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Andal\">Andal</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Rivermen\" title=\"Rivermen\">Rivermen</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">Family</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Dynasty</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Teague\" title=\"House Teague\">House Teague</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:#B0C4DE;\">References</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Torrence Teague</b> was an adventurer of uncertain birth who was the eventual victor in the century-long conflict that arose in the <a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">riverlands</a> after the death of King <a href=\"/index.php/Bernarr_II_Justman\" title=\"Bernarr II Justman\">Bernarr II Justman</a>. He was the founder of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Teague\" title=\"House Teague\">House Teague</a> of the riverlands. Having seized a fortune in <a href=\"/index.php/Gold\" title=\"Gold\">gold</a> in an attack upon the <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">westerlands</a>, he used this wealth to bring large numbers of <a href=\"/index.php/Sellswords\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Sellswords\">sellswords</a> from across the <a href=\"/index.php/Narrow_Sea\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Narrow Sea\">Narrow Sea</a>. After six years of war, Torrence was crowned <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Trident\" title=\"King of the Trident\">King of the Trident</a> at <a href=\"/index.php/Maidenpool\" title=\"Maidenpool\">Maidenpool</a>. However, he was so little loved he was forced to keep sons and daughters of the riverlords as hostages to ensure their loyalty.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_riverlands.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Torrence_Teague&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"6\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border: 2px solid black; padding: 0.2em;&#160;;\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Torrence</a></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td></tr><tr align=\"center\"></tr>\n<tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border-right:1px dashed black\"><div style=\"width:1em;height:2em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:1em;height:2em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"></td></tr><tr align=\"center\"></tr>\n<tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><sp